These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
