| Job   | photographer | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Birthday   | september | january |

